		About Us
	</div>
	<div id="e37" class="panel_box"></div>
	<div id="e36" class="info">
<p>
All too often, a client gets lost in the wheels of justice as they slowly grind their way through a lawsuit.  Promises of a large recovery many times results in an even larger disappointment, as the "cost of litigation", potential defenses and other legal obstacles are not discussed prior to the beginning of the suit.
</p>

<p>
The reality of a lawsuit is difficult at best, and approaching a legal matter being well informed can lessen the stress that is usually associated with litigation.  Talking to a paralegal or a specialist at your attorneys office is never a substitute for talking directly with your attorney.
</p>

<p>
Our office has over 30 years experience in handling injury claims caused by auto collisions, work related accidents, slip and falls, product related accident as well as construction and subrogation matters.
</p>
